  "title": "Material Coordinator/Warehouseman (Entry Level to Senior)",
  "description": "<p>Handle all stores related issues such as goods receipts, proper location of inventory in the warehouse, good issues, inventory control and reporting, shipping including packing</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>GCE ‘O’ / ‘N’ / NITEC</li>\n  <li>2 years’ experience in handling material issue/receipt/delivery and performing monthly cycle count</li>\n  <li>Holds a valid Forklift Certificate</li>\n  <li>Class 3 driving license will be preferred</li>\n  <li>Ability to work independently with minimum supervision in a machine shop environment</li>\n  <li>Ability to perform shift work</li>\n  <li>Experience in SAP Warehouse Management systems preferred</li>\n  <li>Experience in carrying out cycle counts and  investigating inventory discrepancies</li>\n  <li>Able to work independently on packing and verification of materials for shipping purposes</li>\n  <li>Experience in receiving processes</li>\n</ul>",
